properties.Name: Jinguji Home
properties.Notes: Masaye says the house was across the street from the Tofu Store on 1131 Market St. Morrison (1993, 58) lists the Jinguji family at 1728 Fawcett Avenue

properties.Name: New Tacoma Hotel, Watanabe Dentist Office, and Warashima Dentist Office
properties.Source: Morrison (1993, 56) Ito (1973), Ryo Munekata Interview, and Polk's 1929 Tacoma City Directory page 867
properties.Notes: 'We moved to another hotel between 13th and 15th on Broadway, Called the New Tacoma Hotel'-Ryo Munekata

properties.Name: Kawano Home
properties.Notes: 'I had, grew up with five siblings. It was really six, but one little girl died when I was only an infant. So there were five children, three girls and two boys. And a mother and father.' -Harue Kawano, March 11, 2005

properties.Name: Mieko Home
properties.Notes: Morrison (1993, 59) lists the Omori family at this address.

properties.Name: St Paul Lumber Company, House 11
properties.Notes: At a different time, the family lived in house 14.
